{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1080,"text":"What if you could make\nyour sleep more efficient?"},{"time":5400,"text":"As a sleep scientist,"},{"time":7160,"text":"this is the question\nthat has captivated me"},{"time":10080,"text":"for the past 10 years."},{"time":12360,"text":"Because while the lightbulb\nand technology have brought about a world"},{"time":16960,"text":"of 24-hour work and productivity,"},{"time":20440,"text":"it has come at the cost"},{"time":22120,"text":"of our naturally occurring\ncircadian rhythm"},{"time":25440,"text":"and our body's need for sleep."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28520,"text":"The circadian rhythm dictates\nour energy level throughout the day,"},{"time":32479,"text":"and only recently we've been conducting\na global experiment on this rhythm,"},{"time":37360,"text":"which is putting our sleep health"},{"time":39440,"text":"and ultimately\nour life quality in jeopardy."},{"time":44240,"text":"Because of this,"},{"time":45520,"text":"we aren't getting the sleep we need,"},{"time":47680,"text":"with the average American\nsleeping a whole hour less"},{"time":51440,"text":"than they did in the 1940s."}]},{"cues":[{"time":53960,"text":"For some reason,"},{"time":55240,"text":"we decided to wear it as a badge of honor"},{"time":57520,"text":"that we can get by on not enough sleep."},{"time":60400,"text":"This all adds up to a real health crisis."},{"time":64879,"text":"Most of us know that poor sleep\nis linked to diseases"},{"time":68560,"text":"like Alzheimer's, cardiovascular disease,"},{"time":71320,"text":"stroke and diabetes."},{"time":73880,"text":"And if you go untreated\nwith a sleep disorder like sleep apnea,"},{"time":77720,"text":"you're more likely\nto get many of these illnesses."},{"time":81080,"text":"But did you know about sleep's impact\non your mental states?"},{"time":86360,"text":"Poor sleep makes us\nmake risky, rash decisions"},{"time":90760,"text":"and is a drain\non our capacity for empathy."},{"time":94720,"text":"When sleep deprivation literally makes us\nmore sensitive to our own pain,"},{"time":100160,"text":"it's not so surprising that we have\na hard time relating to others"},{"time":104200,"text":"and just generally\nbeing a good and healthy person"},{"time":107440,"text":"when we're sleep-deprived."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109640,"text":"Scientists are now starting to understand"},{"time":112320,"text":"how not only the quantity"},{"time":114520,"text":"but also the quality of sleep\nimpacts our health and well-being."},{"time":120360,"text":"My research focuses"},{"time":122200,"text":"on what many scientists believe\nis the most regenerative stage of sleep:"},{"time":127240,"text":"deep sleep."},{"time":128919,"text":"We now know that generally speaking,"},{"time":131280,"text":"there are three stages of sleep:"},{"time":133920,"text":"light sleep,"},{"time":135280,"text":"rapid eye movement or REM"},{"time":137320,"text":"and deep sleep."},{"time":139080,"text":"We measure these stages by connecting\nelectrodes to the scalp, chin and chest."},{"time":145600,"text":"In light sleep and REM,"},{"time":147080,"text":"our brain waves are very similar\nto our brain waves in waking life."},{"time":151720,"text":"But our brain waves in deep sleep\nhave these long-burst brain waves"},{"time":155840,"text":"that are very different\nfrom our waking life brain waves."},{"time":159000,"text":"These long-burst brain waves\nare called delta waves."},{"time":164600,"text":"When we don't get the deep sleep we need,"},{"time":167080,"text":"it inhibits our ability to learn"},{"time":169280,"text":"and for our cells and bodies to recover."},{"time":172920,"text":"Deep sleep is how we convert\nall those interactions"},{"time":176120,"text":"that we make during the day"},{"time":177840,"text":"into our long-term memory\nand personalities."},{"time":181200,"text":"As we get older,"},{"time":182480,"text":"we're more likely to lose\nthese regenerative delta waves."},{"time":186000,"text":"So in way, deep sleep and delta waves"},{"time":188840,"text":"are actually a marker\nfor biological youth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193680,"text":"So naturally, I wanted to get\nmore deep sleep for myself"},{"time":197240,"text":"and I literally tried almost every gadget,\ngizmo, device and hack out there --"},{"time":202960,"text":"consumer-grade, clinical-grade,"},{"time":204920,"text":"what have you."},{"time":206720,"text":"I learned a lot, and I found\nI really do need, like most people,"},{"time":210560,"text":"eight hours of sleep."},{"time":212240,"text":"I even shifted my circadian component"},{"time":215320,"text":"by changing my meals,\nexercise and light exposure,"},{"time":219040,"text":"but I still couldn't find a way\nto get a deeper night of sleep ..."},{"time":223320,"text":"that is until I met\nDr. Dmitry Gerashchenko"},{"time":226400,"text":"from Harvard Medical School."}]},{"cues":[{"time":228720,"text":"Dmitry told me about\na new finding in the literature,"},{"time":231920,"text":"where a lab out of Germany showed\nthat if you could play certain sounds"},{"time":236360,"text":"at the right time in people's sleep,"},{"time":238920,"text":"you could actually make sleep\ndeeper and more efficient."},{"time":243080,"text":"And what's more, is that this lab showed"},{"time":245760,"text":"that you actually could improve\nnext-day memory performance"},{"time":249280,"text":"with this sound."},{"time":251080,"text":"Dmitry and I teamed up,"},{"time":252480,"text":"and we began working on a way\nto build this technology."},{"time":256000,"text":"With our research lab\ncollaborators at Penn State,"},{"time":260440,"text":"we designed experiments\nin order to validate our system."},{"time":263880,"text":"And we've since received grant funding\nfrom the National Science Foundation"},{"time":267520,"text":"and the National Institute of Health"},{"time":269560,"text":"to develop this deep-sleep\nstimulating technology."},{"time":273480,"text":"Here's how it works."},{"time":275080,"text":"People came into the lab"},{"time":276360,"text":"and we hooked them up\nto a number of devices,"},{"time":278760,"text":"two of which I have on right here --"},{"time":280560,"text":"not a fashion statement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":281840,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":284200,"text":"When we detected\nthat people were in deep sleep,"},{"time":287040,"text":"we played the deep-sleep\nstimulating sounds"},{"time":289720,"text":"that were shown\nto make them have deeper sleep."},{"time":292400,"text":"I'm going to demo this sound\nfor you right now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":296280,"text":"(Repeating sound waves)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":304560,"text":"Pretty weird, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":305840,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":307600,"text":"So that sound is actually at the same\nburst frequency as your brain waves"},{"time":313080,"text":"when your brain is in deep sleep."},{"time":315440,"text":"That sound pattern\nactually primes your mind"},{"time":318720,"text":"to have more of these\nregenerative delta waves."},{"time":322160,"text":"When we asked participants\nthe next day about the sounds,"},{"time":325040,"text":"they were completely unaware\nthat we played the sounds,"},{"time":327960,"text":"yet their brains responded\nwith more of these delta waves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":332280,"text":"Here's an image of someone's brain waves\nfrom the study that we conducted."},{"time":336200,"text":"See the bottom panel?"},{"time":337920,"text":"This shows the sound being played\nat that burst frequency."},{"time":341440,"text":"Now look at the brain waves\nin the upper part of the graph."},{"time":344560,"text":"You can see from the graph"},{"time":346520,"text":"that the sound is actually producing\nmore of these regenerative delta waves."},{"time":352120,"text":"We learned that we could\naccurately track sleep"},{"time":354960,"text":"without hooking people up to electrodes"},{"time":357680,"text":"and make people sleep deeper."},{"time":360800,"text":"We're continuing to develop"},{"time":362240,"text":"the right sound environment\nand sleep habitat"},{"time":365680,"text":"to improve people's sleep health."}]},{"cues":[{"time":368640,"text":"Our sleep isn't\nas regenerative as it could be,"},{"time":372280,"text":"but maybe one day soon,"},{"time":374120,"text":"we could wear a small device"},{"time":376560,"text":"and get more out of our sleep."}]},{"cues":[{"time":379040,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":380280,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}